Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.37,0:00:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 4: Remnants of a Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been more than half a year since Beth bit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.23,0:00:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't know traces of the bite were still inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is what it looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took this sample from my blood three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is a sample from the victims in this recent case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look very similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. This is probably the common vampire gene factor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.29,0:00:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who has this can be controlled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is how Liz was able to possess you,\Neven though it was Beth who bit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have never heard of this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is scientifically very significant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Liz had lived longer, we could\Nhave taken more samples.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.43,0:01:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.81,0:01:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't risk putting any more lives in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.31,0:01:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.65,0:01:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was starting to become a mad scientist there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway, without your purification serum,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it would have been difficult to collect this data.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.88,0:01:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it did contaminate the data a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still got results.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I tested my own blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.34,0:01:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the sample from three days ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this is the sample from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like this will be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I intend to carefully study the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So everything is settled, or at least I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-sama. What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-sama, your eyes... It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.59,0:02:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me, Gen-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.77,0:02:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.87,0:02:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-sama, please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Beth's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoku Gosenzo San'e
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he was getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, he was getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His genes were even stronger than I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was everything I did to this point futile?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have faith in the power of Gen's life force!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me. It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to take my son home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if I should visit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Yoshino-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Liz is alive. Hiraga-kun's live in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl named Shirakura Yoshino gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:06:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she knows the name "Liz," I doubt it's a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how much she knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how she knows Gen is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose we'll have to ask her directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult enough to keep up with Gen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now Liz as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things just aren't going our way, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a big house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen's grandma is the school commissioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's a rich boy, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makes me nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your first time here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.27,0:06:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what else could I do? So I carried him to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop talking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To preserve your good name, I'll end the story here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.39,0:07:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wanna hear more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the last time, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Gen, you're so cute when you're mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad to see you looking well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were really worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need to be hospitalized again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well, if Gen keeps being so nasty to women,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he might have to be hospitalized again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. I promise I'll take good care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's from when you were hospitalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I took that with my doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Kimble and Dr. Casey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other one was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I think it was Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. Elizabeth Bartley!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the other doctors called her Liz.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Liz"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.92,0:08:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.59,0:08:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-sama, it is time for your medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah yes, we've excited him too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.47,0:08:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He needs to take his medicine and rest. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of us can go to the other room\Nand continue our conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again? Don't tell them gross stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two... I'm glad you came to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with you here, it's like we're back in the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real commissioner is on sabbatical.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you're related to Gen's grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.21,0:09:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itoh-san, how have you been feeling lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any more fainting spells?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.01,0:09:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your symptoms could return at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you mustn't grow complacent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.52,0:09:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just received some effective medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. My colleague from Howard U sent it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd get medicine\Nwhen visiting a sick friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is kind of funny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a bit tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a bit of a sedative in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, you can sleep a little if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Yoshino?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:09:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Liz, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with telling us about it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liz sleeps most of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though she sometimes wakes up a little to spy on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.07,0:10:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Spy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not right now. So we can still talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first thing I want to clarify is this:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liz is the same Elizabeth Bartley who\Nworked at Howard U with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seemed normal enough... though not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She isn't human.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I witnessed her attacking someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right in front of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you couldn't stop her from doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I wasn't blaming you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wondering what actually happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liz is a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was violent and selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She never listened to anything I said to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told her to stop over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.38,0:11:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... then she kept doing so many\Nhorrible things! Even to you, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm so sorry, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liz told me she was born with both\Nvampire and human genes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means that she's not a complete vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She needs a certain kind of blood to sustain her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so she went after Gen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:12:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back at the hospital, she said, "At last I've found him!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I begged her, over and over again,\Nto stop hurting people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whenever I did, Liz always said, "Okay, I'll stop."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at this rate, Hiraga-kun's life will be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.27,0:12:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will I die?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live a long life... just like Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Yoshino-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your story has helped us a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there is still one thing you're not telling us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect you're hiding it specifically from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But may I ask you directly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Liz right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're going to protect Gen from Liz,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we need to strike first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:12:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know where she's hiding, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the most important piece of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us! Where is Liz right now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakurako-sensei, this girl has a weak constitution.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we should...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for pushing you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rain has become heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should stay here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll prepare a room immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue this conversation tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Dear Grandma,\NYesterday, something very sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just found out that Elizabeth Bartley\Nleft Tokyo University two months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, they don't know where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the university is no help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liz and Yoshino-san sure have a peculiar relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you suppose Yoshino-san knows what Liz\Nis thinking and what happened in her past?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think Liz just told her those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:16:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought at first that Yoshino-san was being used.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But thinking of it from Liz's point of view,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why would she confide in someone\Nas fragile as Yoshino-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a good point there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds almost like they've been\Nfriends for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, perhaps more than friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you. I've always loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You never noticed, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I always looked only at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you were happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you, were sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter the situation, your eyes were always gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:16:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I loved your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know that you prefer Ayumi-chan and Jennifer-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For tonight please be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment I saw you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that wasn't the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was in the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you were always by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered, Elizabeth Bartley.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Liz. You are Liz, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not. I'm Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please believe me. I'm not Liz. I'm Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please. Make love to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you make love to me, I can remain myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More. Kiss me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're beautiful. I always dreamed of doing this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of giving my whole self to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! I love you, Gen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.14,0:18:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait anymore. Come. Hurry, inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to complete me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel it. Your strong life force.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.28,0:18:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside of me... Lots...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More! Give me more, Gen! More!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Gen...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not there. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.10,0:19:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That tickles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Stop. No, don't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should have noticed it sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.49,0:19:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yoshino's dark aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The countless patients who have lost their energy.\NThe answer was right there in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen. Do you love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you're doing this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't. Not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.93,0:19:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Gen! I feel like I'm losing my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Very good. Nice eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:19:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was waiting for those eyes to emerge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it now! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that, Liz! How cruel! You're so cruel, Liz.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not now. No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen! Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen! Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?\NGen! Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.89,0:20:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress, Gen-sama is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen! Gen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch. You're my own kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.93,0:21:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hinder me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still in the middle of a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.02,0:21:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.49,0:21:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When one of us is in the forefront, the other is asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We both agreed to that rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who broke the rule first was you, Liz!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.25,0:21:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stole my body all the time and did horrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You placed the whole school in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And in order to regain the energy you kept depleting,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up killing so many trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason I was able to last as long as I did
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was because I believed you were my one true friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.69,0:22:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, you betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.86,0:22:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised you wouldn't touch Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong, Yoshino. I didn't betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.20,0:22:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did all of this for both of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.45,0:22:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If our body is complete, there will be nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.71,0:22:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can live in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.79,0:22:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.04,0:22:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.69,0:22:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen, please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.73,0:22:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.86,0:22:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Yoshino-san, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.24,0:22:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.62,0:22:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can find a way for you to coexist with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.54,0:22:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.79,0:22:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay? Yoshino-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.62,0:23:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use, Sensei. Liz is still alive in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.92,0:23:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When night falls again, she might wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.21,0:23:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.80,0:23:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must end things.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.59,0:23:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun... is so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.39,0:23:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.98,0:23:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Gen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.44,0:23:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.74,0:23:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you! You think you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.45,0:23:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.50,0:23:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I can find energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.63,0:23:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.96,0:23:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.42,0:23:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a horrible fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.67,0:23:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen! Why so sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.01,0:23:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I feared. It's just as I feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.10,0:24:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liz's vampire genes have merged with Gen's DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.56,0:24:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His body was unprepared for such a drastic change.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.27,0:24:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's rejecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.81,0:24:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then if this keeps up, will Gen...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.94,0:24:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will he become immortal like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.24,0:24:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.49,0:24:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I must not let that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.16,0:24:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! The purification serum.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.74,0:24:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might be able to reverse the vampire genes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.08,0:24:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jennifer, bring me the medicine at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.33,0:24:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.71,0:24:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress, do you think that will really save Gen-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.67,0:24:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the best case scenario, he will\Nbe able to live a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.09,0:24:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about the worst case scenario?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.60,0:24:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will not be able to let him live.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.43,0:24:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.31,0:24:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only way for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.02,0:24:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want Gen to undergo the same fate as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.69,0:24:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the alternative is living with my curse,\Ndying right now is much easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.70,0:24:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen... You must be in pain, you poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.37,0:25:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will get better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.37,0:25:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.04,0:25:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.79,0:25:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would rather live with you forever.\NI don't want to die now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.93,0:25:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.43,0:25:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.97,0:25:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That we'd be together forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.56,0:25:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.27,0:25:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.82,0:25:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.15,0:25:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.79,0:25:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.78,0:26:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.29,0:26:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.00,0:27:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really have no regrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.75,0:27:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.63,0:27:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I promise you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.67,0:28:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be together forever.
